briefTitle: Immune-Related Trafficking and Signaling in Human Skin Associated With Low-Power, Infrared Laser Treatment
officialTitle: Immune-Related Trafficking and Signaling in Human Skin Associated With Low-Power, Infrared Laser Treatment

protocolDocument.label: Study Protocol, Statistical Analysis Plan, and Informed Consent Form

eligibilityCriteria.criteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* Adult men and women with skin type 1 and 2
* Not pregnant

Exclusion Criteria:

* Use of systemic steroids, topical steroids, tanning solutions and anticoagulant
* History of HIV, mentally incompetent, prisoner, alcohol or drug impairment
* Abnormal photosensitivity

primary.measure: Change in Skin Tissue Response to a Vaccine
primary.description: Change in inflammatory cells with low level laser will be measured.
